{"lemma":"جَمْعُ","slug":"جَمْعُ","root":"ج.م.ع","root_slug":"ج-م-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَمْع","root":"جمع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":13},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":19},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6304","n6305","n6310","n6312","n6313"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to gather, assemble, keep together, to collect","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"ويشار بحسب المجلة، بان اعداد إرهابيي داعش الأجانب ما زال كبيرا جدا على الرغم من التقديرات التي ترجح مقتل الآلاف منهم، حيث تظهر البيانات المجموعة من 33 دولة لها مواطنين يقاتلون مع عصابات داعش الإرهابية، ان ما يزيد عن 6000 منهم قد تمكنوا من العودة الى بلدانهم، فيما تصل اعداد الغائبين إلى الآلاف المضاعفة.","english":"It is shown by the magazine that the number of foreign ISIS terrorists has not ceased to be very large in spite of assessments that affirm the death of thousands of them as likely, whereas the data gathered from 33 states to which citizens fighting for terrorist ISIS groups belong reveals that more than 6000 of them have had the opportunity of returning to their homelands, while the number of absentees has reached several thousands."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to unite, to reconcile","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect oneself, to recollect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lie with"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to add"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to form the plural"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to contain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be full-grown"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have two or more negative attributes at the same time; to have a negative attribute on top of another negative attribute","examples":[{"text":"جَمَعَ بَيْنَ الْجَهْلِ وَﺳُﻮء الْخُلُق","english":"Not only was he ignorant but also ill-mannered"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to assemble","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَمَعَ (jamaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gathering, collecting","examples":[{"text":"جَمْعُ المَال","english":"raising money; collecting money"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crowd, throng, mass, legion","examples":[{"text":"جَمْعٌ مِنَ النَاس","english":"a gathering of people"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a military force"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural, a form of a noun denoting multiples by its sense","examples":[{"text":"جَمْع رُوح أَرْوَاح","english":"the plural of \"rūḥ\" is \"arwāḥ\""}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"addition","examples":[{"text":"الجَمْع وَالطَرْح","english":"addition and subtraction"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lumping together, putting subjects in the same category"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a proposition in which a general and a particular subject are included in one category or judgement through a common attribute"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distribution of a term"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Harsusi [script needed] (egtōma), Mehri عَتمَأ (gatmaʾ).\n\nIntensive of جَمَعَ (jamaʕa)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.ma.ʕa/","/d͡ʒam.ma.ʕa/","/d͡ʒamʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6304","headword_ar":"جَمَعَ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected; brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered, together; gathered up; assembled; congregated; mustered; drew together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Er-Rághib, B, K; *) a thing; (Er-Rághib, Msb, B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the several parts or portions became near together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, B;) or a thing in a scattered, or dispersed, state; (Fr, S;) and a number of men; (Fr;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~E","text_ar":"جمّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [or this has only an intensive signification;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjmE","text_ar":"اجمع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also the inf. n.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below; and] see 2; and 10. ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa bayonahumaA","text_ar":"جَمَعَ بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought them two together, into a state of union, after separation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reconciled them; conciliated them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, united, connected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"formed a connexion between, them two:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 3 (last sentence) in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dnw","text_ar":"دنو"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi viyaAbahu","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ ثِيَابَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attired himself with, his clothes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEati AljaAriyapu","text_ar":"جَمَعَتِ الجَارِيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The girl put on the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diroE","text_ar":"دِرْع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaAr","text_ar":"خِمَار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miloHafap","text_ar":"مِلْحَفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) i. e., (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became a young woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became full-grown."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA jamaEotu","text_ar":"مَا جَمَعْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA@moraA^apK qaT~u","text_ar":"بِا@مْرَاَةٍ قَطُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani A@moraA^apK","text_ar":"عَنِ ا@مْرَاَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have never gone in to a woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have never had a woman conducted to me as my bride."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA@jomaEuwA","text_ar":"فَا@جْمَعُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kayodakumo","text_ar":"كَيْدَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fajamaEa kayodahu","text_ar":"فَجَمَعَ كَيْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa A^amorahu","text_ar":"جَمَعَ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b8-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He composed, arranged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"settled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing, or an affair; as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa A@ll~`hu $amolahu","text_ar":"جَمَعَ ا@للّٰهُ شَمْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ml","text_ar":"شمل"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b9-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It comprised, comprehended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contained."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b10-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pluralized"},{"kind":"text","text":"a word;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have a plural,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plurals."},{"kind":"text","text":"(The Lexicons passim.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","TA","K"]},{"entry_id":"n6305","headword_ar":"جمّع","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajomiyEN","text_ar":"تَجْمِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected; brought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gathered, together; gathered up; assembled; congregated; mustered; drew together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus I render"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as explained above;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much; with much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extraordinary, energy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effectiveness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like; vigorously;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in civ. 2; Msb, K.) Thus in the Kur [civ. 2],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al~a*iY jam~aEa maAlFA waEad~adahu","text_ar":"الَّذِى جَمَّعَ مَالًا وَعَدَّدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Bd)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Who hath collected much wealth, and hath made it a provision for the casualties of fortune,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckoned it time after time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who hath amassed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accumulated, wealth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who hath gained, acquired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earned, wealth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; thus differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained above: but it is allowable to say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlFA","text_ar":"مَالًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", without teshdeed; (Fr;) and thus it is [generally] read in this passage of the Kur. (Bd.) See also 1. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~aEato","text_ar":"حَمَّعَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n. as above, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a hen)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected her eggs in her belly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~aEuwA","text_ar":"جَمَّعُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n. as above, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They were present on the Friday,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the congregation"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"then collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and performed the prayers"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the congregation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on that day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh.) ―         -b4-  Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aw~alu jumoEapK jum~iEato fiY","text_ar":"اَوَّلُ جُمْعَةٍ جُمِّعَتْ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_isolaAmu baEoda Almadiynapi bijuw^aAviY","text_ar":"الاـِسْلَامُ بَعْدَ المَدِينَةِ بِجُوَاثِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first Friday that was observed by the performance of congregational prayer in"},{"kind":"text","text":"the time of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Islám, after"},{"kind":"text","text":"the observance thereof in"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"El-Medeeneh, was in Ju-áthà"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Fr","Msb","K","Bd","TA","S","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n6310","headword_ar":"جَمْعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1. (S, &c.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu AljamoEi","text_ar":"يَوْمُ الجَمْعِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day of resurrection"},{"kind":"text","text":"[when all mankind will be collected together]. (IDrd, K.) ―         -b2-  Also, without the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A name of El-Muzdelifeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"[between 'Arafát and Minè]; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) determinate, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarafaAtu","text_ar":"عَرَفَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) so called because people collect themselves there; (S, Msb;) or because Adam there met with Eve (Mgh, Msb) after they had fallen [from Paradise]: (TA:) [or, app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a name of the tract from 'Arafát to Minè inclusive of these two places:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu jamoEK","text_ar":"يَوْمُ جَمْعٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day of 'Arafeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"[when the pilgrims halt at Mount 'Arafát]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmu jamoEK","text_ar":"اَيَّامُ جَمْعٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the days of Minè."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, K.) ―         -b3-  As an inf. n. used as a subst., properly so termed, (S, * Mgh, Msb,) it also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A collection; a number together; an assembly; a company, troop, congregated"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collective body, party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"group; a mass;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAEapN","text_ar":"جَمَاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, L, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEN","text_ar":"مَجْمَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomiEN","text_ar":"مَجْمِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEapN","text_ar":"مَجْمَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) but ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAEapN","text_ar":"جَمَاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collection, a number together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assemblage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of other things than men; [of beasts, as camels, horses and the like, bulls and cows, and antelopes, gazelles, &c., i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a herd, troop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drove;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dogs, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pack;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of sheep and goats, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of birds, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a flock"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bevy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of bees, and locusts, &c., i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a swarm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and even of trees, and of plants; (L, TA;) it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assemblage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aggregate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any things,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of many"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of few;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) [as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomuwEN","text_ar":"مَجْمُوعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEN","text_ar":"مَجْمَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a number, a plurality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a multitude,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any things: (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumuwEN","text_ar":"جُمُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh, Msb, K.) ―         -b4-  And particularly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An army; a military force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) Whence the phrase, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu sahomN jamoEN","text_ar":"لَهُ سَهْمٌ جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or, more probably,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahomu","text_ar":"سَهْمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEK","text_ar":"جَمْعٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"For him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or shall be, the like of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an army's share"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the spoil. (TA.) ―         -b5-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plural"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing [or word; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a proper plural,"},{"kind":"text","text":"according to the grammarians; and also applied by the lexicologists to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quasi-plural noun,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which the grammarians distinguish by the terms"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisomu jamoEK","text_ar":"اِسْمُ جَمْعٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN lugawiY~N","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ لُغَوِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEN","text_ar":"جِمَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", except that this last is what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisomN laAzimN","text_ar":"اِسْمٌ لَازِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning a subst. which does not govern another as its complement in the gen. case like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEN","text_ar":"جِمَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"do, being thus likened to what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN laAzimN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ لَازِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. an intransitive verb; so that you say of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxibaA='u","text_ar":"الخِبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for instance,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljamiyEu AlA^axobiyapu","text_ar":"الجَمِيعُ الاَخْبِيَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the plural is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAxbyp","text_ar":"الاخبية"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for in this manner I always find it used when it has this signification, which is frequently the case in several of the older lexicons, and in some others; not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEu AlxibaA='i AlA^axobiyapu","text_ar":"جَمِيعُ الخِبَا=ءِ الاَخْبِيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) [whereas] you say, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEu AlxibaA='i AlA^axobiyapu","text_ar":"جَمْعُ الخِبَا=ءِ الاَخْبِيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEu","text_ar":"جِمَاعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxibaA='i AlA^axobiyapu","text_ar":"الخِبَا=ءِ الاَخْبِيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoE","text_ar":"جَمْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plural"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxbA'","text_ar":"الخباء"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxibaA='i","text_ar":"الخِبَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K) for ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljimaAEu","text_ar":"الجِمَاعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comprises a number"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of things]. (S, K.) See also this last word below. ―         -b6-  And see also the next paragraph, in three places. ―         -b7-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"worst sort of dates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) because they are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected together and mixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from among the dates of fifty palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and afterwards, by predominant usage,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":457},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad dates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, * Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain kind of dates"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed together, of several sorts, not in request, and not mixed but for their badness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it signifies, (Mgh, K,) or signifies also, (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, Mgh, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"growing from the date-stones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the name is unknown."},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, Mgh, Msb, K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Red gum;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K;) [app. because"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected and mixed with gum of lighter colour."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b9-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk of any camel having her udder bound with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiraAr","text_ar":"صِرَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; ([i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk that collects in the udder so bound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] that of any camel not having her udder bound therewith is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuwaAqN","text_ar":"فُوَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Mgh","Msb","S","L","K","O","As"]},{"entry_id":"n6312","headword_ar":"جِمْعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in six places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6313","headword_ar":"جُمَعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEaA='u","text_ar":"جَمْعَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajomaEu","text_ar":"اَجْمَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}